# Frontend assets (wwwroot)

## Feature-specific code

- Prefer a feature folder under `wwwroot/<FeatureName>/` for page scripts and helpers.
- Keep feature logic out of vendor trees like `wwwroot/Plugins/` and `wwwroot/Scripts/vendor/`.

## Shared utilities

- Reusable helpers belong under `wwwroot/js/utils/` (for example `dateHelpers.js`, `objectHelpers.js`).

## Conventions

- Use camelCase for variables and functions in hand-written app JavaScript.
- Match existing patterns in the same feature folder (AJAX style, table framework, UI toolkit).
